xslots
======

Example usage: Crack an n-digit code
------------------------------------

```python
from datetime import timedelta
import time

from xslots import Slots

slots = Slots(4, 0, 9, 0)
password = "939614"

start = time.time()
while True:
    print(slots)
    s = "".join(str(slots)))
    
    if s == password:
        end = time.time()
        print(f"Hacked code {s} in {timedelta(seconds = end - start)}")
        break
    
    slots.increase()
```

